<reference id="alt" xml:lang="en-us">
<title><xmlelement>alt</xmlelement></title>
<shortdesc>Alternate text is a textual description of an image that can be read by a screen reader.
        This enables the content and functionality of the image to be accessible to people with
        visual or cognitive disabilities.</shortdesc>
